{"tid":1495187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家還記得國泰是香港公司嗎?","createTime":"2019-08-22T03:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T01:53:29.000Z","uid":190817,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5cce1ed71256a76cba9f81ee4d69c73ddce66f47","tid":1495187,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:14:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SupportFreeHK/videos/1424006117751342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSupportFreeHK%2Fvideos%2F1424006117751342&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIRQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=97cb3878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SupportFreeHK/videos/1424006117751342</a><br />\n<br />\n大家還記得國泰是香港公司嗎?<br />\n<br />\n繼國泰英籍行政總裁何杲、顧客商務總裁盧家培離職後，機艙廣播「香港人加油，萬事小心」機長，國泰證實亦已離職。<br />\n<br />\n超過70年歷史，比中華人民共和國建國還早成立的一間香港公司，正在不斷被外部勢力破壞，對於國泰仲可唔可以「Fly」實在令人痛心！<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，國泰是香港人自豪的品牌，以香港為家，走向國際，香港人出外首選是國泰「I can fly」，正如廣告說【由全球最佳機場出發搭乘全球最佳航空公司】。<br />\n<br />\n希望有一天，香港和國泰可以【為了心中的理想 <br />\n不管阻隔遠或近】再一次向全世界證明【只知天空永遠不分彊界, I can fly】。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acd73074cc054da2258f45449e6abe8dbefc644","tid":1495187,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21add9e04a00410437113f26b6c8bcb7ec63740","tid":1495187,"uid":281926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:19:33.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<spa